Usage: set_virtual_clock_network_parameters [-help] [-cell <string>]
                                            [-clock <string>]
                                            [-library <string>]
                                            [-max_fanout <integer>] [-reset]
                                            [-wire_load_model <string>]

-help                     # Prints out the command usage
-cell <string>            # set list of buffer/inverter (string, optional)
-clock <string>           # list of clocks for buffer insertion
                          # (string, optional)
-library <string>         # set list of library names (string, optional)
-max_fanout <integer>     # maximum fan out (int, optional)
-reset                    # reset all options (bool, optional)
-wire_load_model <string> # set list of wire load model (string, optional)